 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱下半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/555139/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/555139/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃八強抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/592889/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/592889/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃8強已經誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣(日本) vs (香港)朱千雪 首回合:4月4日 次回合:4月10日<br />\nIU(韓國) vs (馬來西亞)林明禎 首回合:4月3日 次回合:4月11日<br />\n林宣妤(馬來西亞) vs (香港)謝安琪 首回合:4月3日 次回合:4月11日<br />\nGal Gadot(以色列) vs (台灣)周子瑜@TWICE 首回合:4月4日 次回合:4月10日<br />\n<br />\n*左方女神先主後客<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲打們到時踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215ea557b295eb9842243766d25df095fe9b1846","tid":603333,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67aac7ca707e045a595a51b7cc86fb0dc83825cd","tid":603333,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86fd34d540c42b182f0f1020eb4efc663810bd5","tid":603333,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T16:52:20.000Z","msg":"清算大會通過